name: NetworkQualityTester
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: network quality tester
des:
This is a part of the simple network quality tester(NQT) . You may use this for reading NQT result, such as Drop and Latency. The NQT has a client for network quality measure, you can implement by your self or use the one we provided, more info can be obtained at http://measure.0io1.com.
How to Use:
On First open , you must use your client to get a id, (see above)
Then Say "Alexa, open Network Quality Tester",
Then Say "Bind YOUR_ID",
Now, you can Say "how is the quality" or "quality" for reading your network quality.
After first bind, Say "quality" is the only need after "open Network Quality Tester".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
